## Example: Selecting by dtype

::: {#62068ac2 .cell execution_count=5}
``` {.python .cell-code}
import polars as pl

df = pl.DataFrame({"A": [[1,2], [1,2,3]], "B": ["A", "B"]})
df.dtypes
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=5}
```
[List(Int64), String]
```
:::
:::


We want to select list columns:

::: {#a668bb07 .cell execution_count=6}
``` {.python .cell-code}
sel = s.has_dtype(pl.List)
SelectCols(cols=sel).fit_transform(df)
```

