## Custom Selectors: Filter by Name

::: {#83ef2721 .cell execution_count=10}
``` {.python .cell-code}
df = pd.DataFrame(
    {
        "patient_id": [101, 102, 103],
        "metric_1": [0.3, 0.3, 0.6],
        "metric_2": [3, 5, 10],
    }
)

selector = s.filter_names(lambda name: name.startswith("metric_"))
s.select(df, selector)
